---
title: Greek-Style Chicken with Pita Bread Salad & Dill Parsley Mayo
description: We love a salad studded with shards of pita bread and crunchy almonds. There's nothing quite like it. Garlicky Greek chicken is topped off with this incredible dill and parsley mayonnaise - you won't know which bit to eat first!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b70fdb3ae08b5661300c492-a8328724.jpg
